docstrings.docstring:
/**
 * Computes the sum of two numbers.
 *
 * This function takes two parameters and returns their sum. It expects both parameters to be numbers.
 *
 * @param {number} param1 - The first number to add.
 * @param {number} param2 - The second number to add.
 * @returns {number} The sum of param1 and param2.
 * @throws {TypeError} If either param1 or param2 is not a number.
 */
